            "description": "Create a new task.\n\n**Required:** `title` (string, max 255 chars)\n**Optional:**\n- `description` — string\n- `status` — `pending` | `in_progress` | `done` (default: `pending`)\n\nThe new task's `id` is automatically saved to the `taskId` variable."
